{"tid":2102713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"致敬！美少女犧牲自己 自願感染肺炎做疫苗試驗","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T17:51:42.000Z","uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49f0839b352cb0aa7d1ed986369667d1edf1a6ef","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6dCbd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6dCbd8.jpg&h=fe0651db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖地牙哥的辛普金斯願意成為新冠人體試驗的一員。"},{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},{"pid":"8d1f2cab9b85c8e73cfc50dcbdf6ce99602cae2e","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情遲未消退，疫苗研發刻不容緩，紐約公益團體1 Day Sooner發起新冠病毒的「人體挑戰測試」（human challenge trial，HCT）在網路上招募自願者，希望透過自願感染者的參與，加快疫苗研發的進程。全美有3000位青年自願參加，包括來自聖地牙哥的100位勇敢的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n聖地牙哥的青年女子辛普金斯（April Simpkins）參加了HCT。現年29歲的她說，自己還年輕，也看不到什麼太大風險，而且疫情散布這麼快，大家當然要想辦法盡快研發出疫苗。"},{"pid":"664d0c518402f6c01755dee29bd4cc1378a114d1","tid":2102713,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"美國少女<br />\n美女老師 美國女老師"},{"pid":"0d147c8b97355cbfa598c9f8dc04ee8244842cdb","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"美🇺🇸少女，你有咩問題？"},{"pid":"9e5249c03888c5aa598f926ebda31705c1b80991","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664d0c518402f6c01755dee29bd4cc1378a114d1","tid":2102713,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"美國少女<br />\n美女老師 美國女老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"啱。<br />\n就好似d新聞成日港女港女咁，條女性格未必港女"},{"pid":"120bd4666b4b35612e03914e5d717576ecded507","tid":2102713,"uid":255525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"大把人中左病毒..唔直接搵病人? 要一個健康既人咁高風險染病..."},{"pid":"a731770d7cfd71a841ab1f4839ba65716caa1999","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"120bd4666b4b35612e03914e5d717576ecded507","tid":2102713,"uid":255525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"大把人中左病毒..唔直接搵病人? 要一個健康既人咁高風險染病..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"洛杉磯時報報導，在美國募集HCT自願者的1 Day Sooner表示，他們主要是找年輕人，因為他們的死亡率低於年長者。不過HCT的風險是，自願者原本都沒有感染新冠病毒，必須「人為感染」後才能察覺疫苗是否有用。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過相較於傳統方式，HCT確實較快。 </span><br />\n<br />\n不過，人為染病這點，還是讓某些醫師不太舒服。聖地牙哥加大的臨床與轉化研究所所長菲爾史坦（Gary Firestein）說，除了死亡的疑慮外，還有新冠肺炎可能帶來的慢性病，比如呼吸道疾病。 <br />\n<br />\n菲爾史坦說，對自願者來說，這些後遺症都比實驗成果來得更切身。聖地牙哥加大的另一名教授則說，HCT對自願者沒有任何好處，單純就是「利他」的極大化。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然同為醫界人士，但聖地牙哥加大博士後研究生畢希（Bryan Bishe）則不這麼想，他自願參加HCT的實驗。37歲的他認為，自願感染確實有風險，他也不會天真的認為沒有風險，但這是評估過的風險，而且大家都需要疫苗。"},{"pid":"7c13a2f3ddd2903b0d2cb30d75e027c0cc104a62","tid":2102713,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"RESPECT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46e9c2d66c3dd8925920ef6cb05592e1a6b6955","tid":2102713,"uid":355289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"120bd4666b4b35612e03914e5d717576ecded507","tid":2102713,"uid":255525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"大把人中左病毒..唔直接搵病人? 要一個健康既人咁高風險染病..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"疫苗係防止你中病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3696d6abf09fbcac659f61fb09923ef2961cf3b7","tid":2102713,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫靚女？師兄食開咩咁把炮"},{"pid":"6202f216f5e0e2ebf9574c359b968e10ca805fef","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3696d6abf09fbcac659f61fb09923ef2961cf3b7","tid":2102713,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecf5a9652ac409ea3a1178a4f72e713ed49219b6","tid":2102713,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"美女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫靚女？師兄食開咩咁把炮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"鬼妹黎講算唔錯！"},{"pid":"36a3ce56eaef869dd9413b9956003c058fde4ae4","tid":2102713,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c46e9c2d66c3dd8925920ef6cb05592e1a6b6955","tid":2102713,"uid":355289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"120bd4666b4b35612e03914e5d717576ecded507","tid":2102713,"uid":255525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"大把人中左病毒..唔直接搵病人? 要一個健康既人咁高風險染病..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"疫苗係防止你中病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"疫苗唔係令你中病毒咩"},{"pid":"fddcb92efb09702f77f70e36ad1553dd1832eb41","tid":2102713,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a3ce56eaef869dd9413b9956003c058fde4ae4","tid":2102713,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"q